reviewText: Not that great: it looks like a bunch of guys who can't/won't speak English and who spend much of the video talking instead performing.
Not a movie like I thought it would be.

I really enjoyed this softly erotic production from Vivid :-). To me, anything with Cori Nadine in it is worth 4 stars from 5 and that's what I gave the DVD. The other girls are totally cool and are lovely but the true hottie is Cori ! and at a guess, that's why they put the glamorous fitness woman of the Universe on the cover .... she is HOT. Oh okay the the DVD is really woth 4.5 stars !!!!
